<apex:page standardcontroller="MSATeamingPartner__c" extensions="ECO_MSATeamingPartnerController" action="{!init}">

	<style>
        .customHelpIcon
        {
            display:inline-block;
            margin:0 5px 0 0;
            width:24px;
            height:24px;
            vertical-align:top !important;
        }
        /* CUSTOM HELP / GUIDANCE TEXT BOX */
        .customHelpText{
            padding: 7px;
            border: 1px solid #85B3CE;
            min-height: 10px;
            display: block;
            width: auto;
            margin: 0 0 5px 0;
            background-repeat: no-repeat;
            border-radius: 4px;
            background-color: #A2D3F1;
            
        }
        .customHelpBody{
            display:inline-block;
            color:#;
            max-width:95%;
        }   

	</style>

	<apex:sectionheader title="MSA Teaming Partner Edit" subtitle="{!agreement.ContractTitle__c}({!agreement.AgreementNumber__c})"/>
	<apex:form >	
        <div class="customHelpText">
            <div class="customHelpBody">
If applicable, add any teaming partner(s) related to the MSA that Project Managers should be aware of when executing task order projects.  This could include vendors or subs that were included as part of the proposal during pursuit of the MSA and have been approved by the client.  Note any special arrangements with the teaming partner in the Comments field so all project team members are aware of any obligations to the partner.<br/><br/>

Attach any relevant contracts documents with the teaming partner, such as teaming agreements or executed contracts, to the Contracts section on the home page. 
            </div>
        </div> 

	<apex:pageBlock >
		<apex:pageBlockButtons >
			<apex:commandButton value="Save" action="{!save}"/>
			<apex:commandButton value="Return to MSA" action="{!cancel}"/>
		</apex:pageBlockButtons>
			
		<apex:pageBlockSection collapsible="false">
			<apex:inputField value="{!MSATeamingPartner__c.Account__c}"/>
			<apex:inputField value="{!MSATeamingPartner__c.Comments__c}"/>		
		</apex:pageBlockSection>
		
		<apex:pageBlockSection title="Contact Information" collapsible="false">
			<apex:inputField value="{!MSATeamingPartner__c.Contact_Name__c}"/>			
			<apex:inputField value="{!MSATeamingPartner__c.Role__c}"/>		
			<apex:inputField value="{!MSATeamingPartner__c.Phone__c}"/>
			<apex:inputField value="{!MSATeamingPartner__c.Email__c}"/>			
		</apex:pageBlockSection>
		<apex:inputHidden value="{!MSATeamingPartner__c.Agreement__c}"/>
	<!--	<apex:pageBlockSection title="System Information" collapsible="false">
			<apex:outputField value="{!MSATeamingPartner__c.Agreement__c}"/>
		</apex:pageBlockSection>  -->
	</apex:pageBlock>
	</apex:form>
	
</apex:page>